long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This chrome extension is part of the BlinqIO Virtual Tester solution
https://docs.blinq.io
This extension copy your session cookies and format it to a file (env.json).
The env.json in your project will enable the browser to open already authenticated.
